<br/>
<b>Don't know how system works? Read about it.</b><br/><br/>


<b>Profile</b>
<br/>
Displays information supplied during the registration and also allows you to edit your registration details.
<br/><br/>

<b>Home</b>
<br/>
Home page has options to display the latest posts created on the system and also allows you to create your own post to be seen by others.
<br/><br/>
<b>Preview</b>
<br/>
Preview help you see the posts created by you and the posts created by others.
<br/><br/>
<b>Logout</b>
<br/> 

Signs you out of the system. If you want to use the system you have to use the latest user name and password.

 




